Conversion to NeuroML of a model granule cell developed by Volker Steuber and Chiara Saviane.

Based on a granule cell model from Michiel Berends, Neural Comp 15, 2531-47 (2005) originally modified by Chiara Saviane and
further modified by VS, July 2006

For more details see http://opensourcebrain.org/projects/granulecellvscs
